\section{Deuxième triolet - 24/04/2019}

Aborde difficulté d'accentuer la deuxième croche du triolet, surtout en doublant les autres croches et en chantant le konakol. Aborde alors le style Maloya de la Réunion.

\vspace{5mm}
Pattern / Groove en 9/8

\begin{lilypond}[staffsize=18]
  \version "2.18.2"
  \include "general_def.ly"

  %% accent
  act = \markup { \left-align \musicglyph #"scripts.sforzato" }
  
  %% Notes
  maloyaup = \drummode {
    \numericTimeSignature
    \time 9/8
    \override Beam.positions = #'(5 . 5)   %% left right

    \override NoteHead.transparent = ##f
    hh8[ hh-> \override NoteHead.transparent = ##t hh]
    
    \override NoteHead.transparent = ##f
    hh8[ hh^\act \override NoteHead.transparent = ##t hh]
    \override NoteHead.transparent = ##f
    hh8[ hh^\act \override NoteHead.transparent = ##t hh]    

    \bar ".|:"

    \override NoteHead.transparent = ##f
    hh8[ hh^\act sn]
    hh8[ <sn hh>^\act \ghost sn]
    hh8[ hh-> \ghost sn]

    hh8[ hh-> \ghost sn]
    hh8[ <sn hh>-> \ghost sn]
    hh8[ hh-> \ghost sn]

    \bar ":|."
  }
  maloyadw = \drummode {
    s4. s4. s4.

    bd8[ r8 bd8]
    bd4.
    r4.

    bd8[ r8 bd8]
    r4.
    r4.
  }
  
  \score {
    <<
    \new DrumStaff 
    <<
    \set DrumStaff.drumStyleTable = #(alist->hash-table md)
    \new DrumVoice { \voiceOne \maloyaup }
    \new DrumVoice { \voiceTwo \maloyadw }
    >>
    >>
  }
  
\end{lilypond}

Et en parlant de Konakol, regarder la chaîne de \href{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLTDfoneAJ0&list=PLaq6h18rnEfXpwbOWwidMQPUvgds-7LSp}{Asaf Sirkis}.

